headline: Why Are Coinbase (COIN) Shares Soaring Today
summary: Shares of blockchain infrastructure company Coinbase (NASDAQ:COIN) jumped 5.4% in the afternoon session after the major indices rebounded (Nasdaq +1.5%, S&P 500 +1.0%) as reports pointed to easing tensions between Israel and Iran. The Wall Street Journal said senior Iranian officials had signaled a willingness to restart stalled nuclear talks, on the condition that Washington refrain from joining Israel's ongoing strikes.
